videos.description: Malik Newman finds an opening and blows by the Cowboys' defense for a layup.
videos.headline: Kansas' Newman darts through lane for layup

videos.description: Devonte' Graham forces a steal and dishes it to Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk, who throws down a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham steals, Mykhailiuk scores

videos.description: Lagerald Vick drives to the basket and punishes the rim with a strong jam.
videos.headline: Kansas'  Vick drives baseline for dunk
